    <caution>
      <cn>
        <para>
          <text style="1">注意：当进行以下维修工作时,必须严格遵守维护手册及相关维修文件的安全注意事项。</text>
        </para>
      </cn>
      <en>
        <para>
          <text style="1">Caution: When you do the maintenance work, you must obey the safety caution of the AMM and maintenance documents.</text>
        </para>
      </en>
    </caution>
    <explain>
      <item path="000013000001000001" no="1">
        <cn>
          <para align="1">
            <text style="1" color="000000">每</text>
            <text style="2" color="000000">年</text>
            <text style="4" color="000000">11</text>
            <text color="FF0000">月</text>
            <text color="000000" bgcolor="FF00FF">1</text>
            <text color="000000" issuber="True">日</text>
            <text color="000000" issuper="True">至</text>
            <text fontname="Wingdings" color="000000">%</text>
            <text color="000000">次</text>
            <text color="000000">4月30日期间所有出发的极地航班，或该时段之外遇有预测航路中的大气温度达到-65℃或更低时，执行极地航线任务的飞机在飞行前完成用于冰点测试的燃</text>
            <text color="000000">油取样工作
</text>
            <text islinestarttype="1" linestartsign="#4E004F00540045003A00" fontname="Arial" linestartsgmllistname="Note" style="5">Ø</text>
            <text color="000000" islinestarttype="1" linestartsign="#4E004F00540045003A00">323</text>
          </para>
        </cn>
        <en>
          <para>
            <text color="000000">From November 1ST to following April 30th every year, all flights takeoff from airport for cross-polar operation; or other periods that the route atmospheric temperature are predicted to reached -65 degrees orlower，Sample the fuel for freezing test before the takeoff of the cross-polar flight.</text>
          </para>
        </en>
      </item>
      <item path="000013000001000002" no="2">
        <cn>
          <para>
            <text color="000000">在北京机场，取样设备由北京飞机维修工程有限公司提供。</text>
          </para>
        </cn>
        <en>
          <para>
            <text color="000000">At Beijing airport, Ameco provide sampling equipment.</text>
          </para>
        </en>
      </item>
    </explain>
    <explain>
      <item path="000013000002000001" no="1">
        <cn>
          <para>
            <text color="000000">取样设备包括标准带盖油样瓶（4 个）、一个足够大容器用以储存取样前冲洗管路的废油、注射器型取样器、开关阀门和软管</text>
          </para>
        </cn>
        <en>
          <para>
            <text color="000000">Sampling equipment includes standard fuel sample bottles with lid, a container,which is big enough to store the fuel waste which is put out when fuel pipes arerinsed before sample is taken, samplers of injector type, switch valve and softpipes</text>
          </para>
        </en>
      </item>
    </explain>
